queries.sql: SELECT id,influencer_id,network,create_date, rawdata,follower,week(create_date) AS week,month(create_date) AS month,year(create_date) AS year,day(create_date) AS day FROM influencer_stat_post_recent_intern WHERE id > 0 ORDER BY id ASC LIMIT 0,500
